<h1> EACL 2009: LOCATION AND DATES </h1>

<p>
EACL 2009 will take place in Athens (Greece) and the structure of the
programme is as follows:
</p>


<ul>
<li> Monday, March 30 ------ Tutorials and workshops
<li> Tuesday, March 31 ----- Tutorials and workshops
<li> Wednesday, April 1 ---- Main conference
<li> Thursday, April 2 -------- Main conference
<li> Friday, April 3 ------------ Main conference
</ul>

<p>
A call for papers for the main conference will be issued around April
2008, with a submission deadline in November 2008.
</p>

<p>
Please put the dates for the conference in your diaries!
</p>

